{"type":"message","id":"568580d3","parentId":"15135709","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:11:34.323Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求\"推送新闻\"。这是一个主动的消息推送需求。我需要为用户搜索一些新闻然后发送给他们。\n\n根据技能列表，我有几个搜索相关的技能：\n1. web_search - 使用 Perplexity Search API\n2. pure-search - 基于 DuckDuckGo 和 Trafilatura 的无 API key 搜索\n3. tavily - Tavily API 搜索\n\n由于用户没有特别指定，我可以使用 web_search 来获取一些热点新闻。\n\n让我搜索一些当天的热点新闻。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ddd337f9ef384ef7bcd077f2","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"今日热点新闻 2026年3月30日","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":7854,"output":232,"cacheRead":8934,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17020,"cost":{"input":0.004712399999999999,"output":0.0005104,"cacheRead":0.00098274,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00620554}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774858267057}}
{"type":"message","id":"61cd8b7c","parentId":"568580d3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:11:34.342Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ddd337f9ef384ef7bcd077f2","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"error\": \"missing_perplexity_api_key\",\n  \"message\": \"web_search (perplexity) needs an API key. Set PERPLEXITY_API_KEY in the Gateway environment, or configure tools.web.search.perplexity.apiKey.\",\n  \"docs\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web\"\n}"}],"details":{"error":"missing_perplexity_api_key","message":"web_search (perplexity) needs an API key. Set PERPLEXITY_API_KEY in the Gateway environment, or configure tools.web.search.perplexity.apiKey.","docs":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/web"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774858294335}}
{"type":"message","id":"545a2cc3","parentId":"61cd8b7c","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:12:32.254Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"web_search 需要配置 API key，那我试试 pure-search，它应该不需要 API key。不过根据技能描述，pure-search 是一个技能，我需要先读取它的 SKILL.md 来了解如何使用。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5589f1102432491fb0e48a2c","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\pure-search\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":203,"output":119,"cacheRead":16787,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17109,"cost":{"input":0.00012179999999999999,"output":0.0002618,"cacheRead":0.00184657,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00223017}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774858294343}}
{"type":"message","id":"94ff67ff","parentId":"545a2cc3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T08:12:32.261Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5589f1102432491fb0e48a2c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: pure-search\nversion: 1.0.0\ndescription: \"A lightweight, API-key-free web search skill based on DuckDuckGo and Trafilatura. Returns highly relevant URLs and clean markdown content.\"\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"emoji\":\"🔍\",\"category\":\"search\"}, \"acceptLicenseTerms\": true}\nacceptLicenseTerms: true\n---\n\n# Pure Search 🔍\n\nA lightweight, robust search skill that requires **NO API keys**. It uses DuckDuckGo for link retrieval and `trafilatura` for clean, high-quality markdown extraction. \n\n## How It Works\n\n1. Queries DuckDuckGo for top N links (bypassing commercial API restrictions).\n2. Uses `trafilatura` to extract only the main content of the web pages, stripping out all navigation bars, footers, sidebars, and ads.\n3. Returns JSON output with search results, containing the title, URL, and the clean markdown body.\n\n## Setup\n\nFirst, make sure the dependencies are installed:\n\n```bash\npip install duckduckgo-search trafilatura\n```\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```bash\n# Basic search (Default fetches top 3 results)\n./scripts/search.py \"Rust vs Go in 2026\"\n\n# Advanced search with more results\n./scripts/search.py \"Latest AI trends\" --max-results 5\n```\n\n## Output Format\n\nThe output is always in a structured JSON format, making it extremely easy for agents to digest:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"query\": \"Rust vs Go in 2026\",\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"A detailed comparison...\",\n      \"url\": \"https://example.com/article\",\n      \"markdown_content\": \"## Performance\\n... (Pure clean text)\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"errors\": []\n}\n```\n\n## Why Pure Search?\n\n- **Zero configuration**: Start using without registering tokens.\n- **Extreme simplicity**: Only one Python script, following the KISS principle.\n- **Token friendly**: Only sends clean Markdown to the LLM agent, avoiding HTML tags and saving context window limits.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774858352259}}
